name: GRR Rapid Response
description: This app implements various actions from the GRR API

actions.description: Validate the asset configuration for connectivity using supplied configuration
List all the connections configured on the device
List all the endpoints/sensors configured on the device

example_values: VMware-56 4d 9f c8 45 f6 ee d0-96 1a ec da 13 1e 13 66

actions.description: Look for files matching given criteria
Retrieve matching regex in a client's browser cache

users.description: Users to query. Use commas to separate

count.description: Max number of items to fetch

created_by.description: Only return hunts created by a give user. If approved_by or/and description_contains are also supplied, then logical AND is applied to all the criterias. NOTE: this filter can only be used in conjunction with 'active_within' filter (to prevent queries of death)

description_contains.description: Only return hunts where description contains given substring (matching is case-insensitive).If created_by or/and approved_by are also supplied, then logical AND is applied to all the criterias. NOTE: this filter can only be used in conjunction with 'active_within' filter (to prevent queries of death)

active_within.description: Only return hunts that were active within given time duration

count.description: Max number of items to fetch
